(s+t)^p\le 2^{p-1}(s^p + t^p)
p\gt1
s+t=1
\min\lbrace t^p+(1-t)^p\rbrace=2^{1-p}
s+t\gt0
 u = \frac{s}{s+t} 
(s+t)^p\le 2^{p-1}(s^p + t^p)  \Leftrightarrow	 \frac{1}{2^{p-1}} \le (\frac{s}{s+t}) ^p + (\frac{t}{s+t}) ^p 
 2^{1-p} \le u^p + (1-u) ^p 
(s+t)^p > 0
1 \leqslant 2^{p-1}\left(\left(\frac{s}{s+t}\right)^p + \left(\frac{t}{s+t}\right)^p\right),
